com.foxhole.tools.spartan.spaces
Class VirtualGameSpace

java.lang.Object
  com.foxhole.tools.spartan.spaces.VirtualGameSpace
All Implemented Interfaces:
INonRenderableSpartanObject, ISpartanObject, IGameSpaceObject
public class VirtualGameSpace
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGameSpaceObject

The vitual gamespace is an form oriented implementation of a gamespace. This gamespace will only serve to hold forms showing a set of virtual representations (forms), hence the virtual part of the name.

Author:
Tiago "Spiegel" Costa
